messages.msgSnippet: Okay, I ve been up for almost 5 days now, Avery is really sick and he s not sleeping for more than a few hours at a streach, my butt is stuck in the computer
messages.messageBody:
Okay, I've been up for almost 5 days now, Avery is really sick and
he's not sleeping for more than a few hours at a streach, my butt is
stuck in the computer chair, his fave place to nurce. I've been
reading all my mail and searching through yahoo groups and decided
today that I wanted to start a few new groups and thought I'd let
ya'll know about them first.

The first group is for California Unschoolers. I've noticed that
there are quite a few folks from Cali o nthis list and there wasn't a
Cali unschooling list so, here ya go

http://groups.yahoo.com/groups/CaliUnschooling


The other group is for Pagan Unschoolers, again a group that I
could't find, lots that cover all methods but none strictly
unschooling, so in my sleep deprived mind I took it upon myself to
start on. :-)

http://groups.com/groups/PaganUnschooling

So, there they are I hope that some of ya drop on by.

I'm gonna try to remove myself from this chair and attempt to lay
Avery down in bed, crossed fingers and toes.

Rebecca
